company_name: FLORUS GARTENBETRIEB GESELLSCHAFT MIT BESCHRÄNKTER HAFTUNG
information: The company FLORUS GARTENBETRIEB GESELLSCHAFT MIT BESCHRÄNKTER HAFTUNG, is a Service Provider, founded in 1977, which operates in the Peat and compost industry. It also operates in the Green-leaf plants industries. It is based in Isernhagen, Germany.
